1) Pull image from docker

2) Run container with following command

    docker run --name some-postgres -p5432:5432  -d postgres

3) Login to container
    docker exec -it -u999 <Container ID> /bin/bash

4) Create user using following command and provide password on prompt

    createuser <username> -P

5) Create database with <username> as owner
    createdb --owner=<username> <db name>

6) Logout from container using ctr+d command

7) Apply database migrations using following command
    ./gradlew -Dflyway.url=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/<db name> -Dflyway.user=<username> -Dflyway.password=<password>  flywayMigrate
